data.description: Captivating 3-Bed, 3-full bath brick ranch home in Monessen! Modern charm flows through the beautiful kitchen and dining area. The finished basement features a bar area that adds a touch of luxury perfect for hosting friends and family. Enjoy the privacy of a fenced yard, and unwind after a long day in the spacious master bedroom with its own master bath. Your dream home awaits!
